y from the generated report as a fallback.\"\"\"\n../1542-c4a3e539/forge/forge_metadata.py:1925:            reason=\"test_generation_failed\",\n../1542-c4a3e539/forge/forge_metadata.py:2006:        \"Analyze the generated tests, metadata, stats, and dynamic-access report in this repository. \"\n../1542-c4a3e539/forge/forge_metadata.py:2010:        \"- Explain briefly why dynamic-access coverage is missing or still very low.\\n\"\n../1542-c4a3e539/forge/forge_metadata.py:2023:    if candidate.reason == \"test_generation_failed\" or candidate.coverage is None:\n../1542-c4a3e539/forge/forge_metadata.py:2029:        f\"Automation completed for `{claimed_issue.issue_coordinates}`, but dynamic-access coverage remains \"\n../1542-c4a3e539/forge/forge_metadata.py:2031:        \"This suggests the generated tests are not exercising the required dynamic-access paths well enough.\\n\\n\"\n../1542-c4a3e539/forge/forge_metadata.py:2033:        \"- Inspect the generated tests and compare them with the dynamic-access report to find uncovered call sites.\\n\"\n../1542-c4a3e539/forge/forge_metadata.py:2144:    coverage_details = \"- Dynamic-access coverage: unavailable\"\n../1542-c4a3e539/forge/forge_metadata.py:2148:            f\"- Dynamic-access coverage: {candidate.coverage.covered_calls}/\"\n../1542-c4a3e539/forge/forge_metadata.py:2312:    if candidate.reason in {\"test_generation_failed\", \"job_failed\"}:\n../1542-c4a3e539/forge/forge_metadata.py:2746:            pipeline_argv.append(\"--keep-tests-without-dynamic-access\")\n../1542-c4a3e539/forge/forge_metadata.py:4799:        \"--keep-tests-without-dynamic-access\",\n../1542-c4a3e539/forge/forge_metadata.py:4802:            \"Forwarded to the new-library pipeline. Keeps generated tests for dynamic-access \"\n../1542-c4a3e539/forge/forge_metadata.py:4803:            \"strategies even when no dynamic-access coverage is added.\"\n../1323-822fdf6a/tests/tck-build-logic/src/main/groovy/org/graalvm/internal/tck/harness/tasks/Anal